### Usterka download
GET http://localhost:8000/usterki/pokoj/101
Accept: application/json

###

### Add new usterka
POST http://localhost:8000/usterki
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "zglaszajacy_id": 1,
  "pokoj_id": 101,
  "opis_usterki": "Zepsuty telewizor",
  "priorytet": "Wysoki",
  "status": "Zgloszona"
}

### Update usterka status
PATCH http://localhost:8000/usterki/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "W_trakcie"
}

### Add new user
POST http://localhost:8000/uzytkownicy
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "imie": "Jan",
  "nazwisko": "Kowalski",
  "email": "jan@akademik.pl",
  "rola": "STUDENT"
  }

### Get new user
GET http://localhost:8000/uzytkownicy/1
Accept: application/json